sql:
SELECT namespace_uri
  FROM namespaces
  WHERE status = 'active';

SELECT COUNT(*) AS active_namespaces_count
  FROM namespaces
  WHERE status = 'active';

SELECT namespace_id, MAX(version_number) AS latest_version
FROM namespace_versions
GROUP BY namespace_id;

SELECT namespace_uri
FROM namespaces
ORDER BY namespace_uri;

external_knowledge:
- Detailed information includes namespace URI, version number, organization name, contact name, job title, phone number, email, assurance level name, and description;
- Latest version refers to the highest version number for each namespace;
- Compliance status refers to the organization's compliance with certain regulatory requirements;
- Assurance level refers to the level of assurance provided by the namespace.

